name: NEW Crystal Shape Bowls
description:
Whoa! Seriously in love with these new mini bowls! Moons, Hearts and Cat Heads made from either Rose Quartz or Quartz! Perfect for storing your small crystals, rings, or other little trinkets. Each piece is unique in shape, size and color due to natural stones. No 2 are alike. 

Moons-3-4"

Hearts 3-4"

Cat Heads  3.5"

Made in Brazil
